Output extract.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 400
Set Padding 15
Set Margin 8
Set Framerate 10
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.9

Hide
Type "bash scripts/pi-json-extract.sh 'write a bash script to check disk usage and alert if above 90%'"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show
Sleep 10s
Sleep 2s
